<br />
<br />
&quot;USA&quot;...ok if you wish I can refer to them as the &quot;<i>ass backward Red States that have fuck all  to do with rest of us for God's sake please</i>!&quot; if you wish? :p<br />
for all the shit we certainly have and the evil crap of the British &quot;system&quot;, the degree off ass backwardness in ex-Confederate states seems appalling :/</div>

